diff --git a/CHANGELOG.md b/CHANGELOG.md
index 12eea34..60ef385 100644
--- a/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -2,6 +2,24 @@
 
 All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
 
-The format is based on *Keep a Changelog* and this project adheres to *Semantic Versioning*.
+The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
+and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
 
-## [Unreleased]
+## [0.2.0] - 2026-03-06
+
+### Added
+- **SubmissionCsvExporter**: Introduced a new robust exporter using `StreamedResponse` for better memory management.
+- **WizardReceiptInterface**: Added a domain-level interface to decouple receipt logic from implementation.
+- **Excel Compatibility**: Added UTF-8 BOM to CSV exports to ensure correct character rendering in Microsoft Excel.
+- **Translated Headers**: Column headers are now dynamically translated using the `yiggle_form_wizard` domain.
+
+### Changed
+- **PriceCalculatorInterface**: Updated return type to `WizardReceiptInterface` to improve abstraction and testability.
+- **Architecture Refactor**: Shifted from generic data-flattening to explicit, field-based export logic.
+- **Test Suite**: Fully refactored Unit and Functional tests for PHPUnit 12 compatibility, including improved type-safety and cache handling.
+
+### Removed
+- **SubmissionFlattener**: This class was removed as its logic is now superseded by the `SubmissionCsvExporter`. This is a **breaking change**.
+
+## [0.1.0] - 2026-03-05
+- Initial release with basic form wizard functionality.
